[Start]
   │
   ▼
[Create .img file]
   │  dd if=/dev/urandom of=cipher.img bs=1M count=1024
   │
   ▼
[Setup LUKS]
   │  sudo cryptsetup luksFormat cipher.img
   │
   ▼
[Open LUKS container]
   │  sudo cryptsetup luksOpen cipher.img secureDisk
   │
   ▼
[Create filesystem inside]
   │  sudo mkfs.ext4 /dev/mapper/secureDisk
   │
   ▼
[Mount filesystem]
   │  mkdir ~/secret-folder
   │  sudo mount /dev/mapper/secureDisk ~/secret-folder
   │
   ▼
[Use container]
   │  # read/write files inside ~/secret-folder
   │
   ▼
[Stop using container]
   │  # make sure no processes are inside
   │
   ▼
[Unmount filesystem]
   │  sudo umount -l ~/secret-folder
   │
   ▼
[Close LUKS container]
   │  sudo cryptsetup luksClose secureDisk
   │
   ▼
[Optional: Delete .img file]
   │  rm cipher.img
   │
   ▼
[End]
